  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 44ff468522a88594f835ce1750834844, type: 3}
  m_Name: LevelUpIntro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
  - Nice work.
  - As you gain experience, I gather more data about your piloting style.
  - I can use this data to improve combat efficiency and mission completion effectiveness.
  - You may roughly equate this to a level-up system.
  - Let's convert some of that experience to an upgrade now.
